Paper: hep-th/9506031

Date: 1995-06-06

Title: Boundary Reflection Matrix for $ade$ Affine Toda Field Theory

Authors: J.D. Kim

Comments: 20 pages, latex, typing errors corrected and a note added

We present a complete set of conjectures for the exact boundary reflectionmatrix for $ade$ affine Toda field theory defined on a half line with theNeumann boundary condition.